title: 1996–97 Deportivo Toluca F.C. season
text:
The <a href="1996%E2%80%9397%20in%20Mexican%20football">1996–97</a> <a href="Deportivo%20Toluca%20F.C.">Deportivo Toluca F.C.</a> season was the 90th season in the <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club's history and the 44th consecutive season in the top flight of <a href="Mexican%20football%20league%20system">Mexican football</a>.
